{"text_id":68689,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," aim"," to"," find"," real","izable"," Hamilton","ians"," that"," can"," be"," used"," for"," universal"," adiabatic"," quantum"," computers","."," Adi","abatic"," quantum"," computing"," is"," a"," promising"," paradigm"," for"," solving"," complex"," problems"," in"," physics",","," materials"," science",","," cryptography",","," and"," optimization","."," However",","," finding"," the"," optimal"," Hamiltonian"," that"," can"," achieve"," universality"," is"," a"," challenging"," task","."," The"," main"," problem"," we"," aim"," to"," solve"," is"," the"," identification"," of"," a"," practical"," Hamiltonian"," that"," can"," be"," implemented"," in"," current"," experimental"," setups"," with"," a"," small"," number"," of"," qu","bits","."," Our"," approach"," is"," based"," on"," a"," systematic"," and"," constructive"," method"," for"," designing"," Hamilton","ians"," that"," can"," emulate"," the"," computation"," of"," any"," quantum"," algorithm","."," We"," show"," that"," by"," using"," a"," particular"," form"," of"," non","-","sto","qu","astic"," Hamilton","ians"," and"," an"," adiabatic"," evolution"," scheme",","," we"," can"," achieve"," universality"," with"," a"," minimal"," number"," of"," qu","bits","."," We"," also"," present"," a"," scalable"," architecture"," that"," can"," be"," used"," to"," implement"," the"," designed"," Hamilton","ians","."," Our"," work"," provides"," a"," significant"," contribution"," to"," the"," field"," of"," adiabatic"," quantum"," computing"," as"," it"," provides"," a"," practical"," and"," efficient"," method"," to"," construct"," real","izable"," Hamilton","ians"," for"," achieving"," universality","."," The"," results"," of"," this"," work"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," enable"," the"," use"," of"," adiabatic"," quantum"," computing"," for"," solving"," practical"," problems"," that"," are"," deemed"," intractable"," by"," classical"," computers","."," Our"," work"," contributes"," to"," the"," ongoing"," effort"," towards"," developing"," efficient"," quantum"," computing"," algorithms"," that"," can"," revolution","ize"," different"," fields"," of"," science"," and"," technology","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}